title: 2nd Annual Night of Strength at Marquee
desc: Thank you for supporting the fight against ALS by attending the 2 nd  Annual Night of Strength Cocktail Reception at  Marquee New York  on Friday, October 16th from 6PM - 10PM.  ? FIGHT.LOVE.LIVE. Spread the word!  ? Net proceeds from donations are not tax deductible as a charitable donation. Those who cannot attend the event and wish to gift additional non-tax deductible funds may also do so via Eventbrite.
